		<div id="comment_body_64137416"><p>Basically what that means in English is that a profession is a job, but most often when people use the word they mean it has training/qualifications.  So while technically you could use it to mean any job is a profession, that would be an uncommon usage of the term</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64137416">

